3) What are the most important features of Kotlin?
The most popular features of kotlin are:

1.Concise: Kam code likhna padta hai.
2.Compact Code: Java se lagbhag 40% kam code hota hai.
3.Simple: Seekhna aur use karna aasan hai.
4.Open Source: Free aur sabke liye available hai.
5.Null Safety: Null errors ko rokta hai.
6.Extensions: Purani class me bina badlav kiye naye features add kar sakte hain.
7.Java Interoperability: Java aur Kotlin ek sath kaam kar sakte hain.
8.Smart Cast: Data type automatically pehchan leta hai.
9.Low Learning Curve: Jaldi seekha ja sakta hai.
10.Compilation Time: Jaldi compile hota hai.
11.Tools-friendly: IDE aur command line dono me support karta hai.
