4) Why did you switch to Kotlin from Java? Why do some developers like to switch to Kotlin from Java?

Kotlin Java se zyada simple aur clean programming language hai. Isme Java ke comparison me kam code likhna padta hai, isliye coding easy ho jati hai. Kotlin me kuch aise features bhi hain jo Java me nahi hain. Android Studio bhi Kotlin ko support karta hai, isliye Android app development ke liye Kotlin ek bahut achhi choice hai aur future me iska use aur bhi badhne wala hai.

